title: Forgotten Skills of Backyard Herbal Healing
description:
Forgotten Skills of Backyard Herbal Healing and Family Health by Caleb Warnock, Kirsten Skirvin

Overview: Modern medicine can work wonders, but most of it has roots in the healing powers you can find in your own backyard. This informative book teaches you to harvest, dry, and store herbs that will keep you healthy. Discover how to use natural remedies safely, so you can nurture your family's wellness without leaving home
